{
  "stem": "268.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And you could have-- have some-- we called it organize.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Organizing means you-- you-- you-- you-- in a way, it means stealing a little bit, too, because if-- if someone-- if the SS [? not was ?] looking and you were loading potatoes, you put some on pocket or start eating.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So it was stealing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But it's called-- we-- every-- every former concentration camp inmate you will speak to will say organizing-- to organize some food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So you could-- you know, there were some-- all kind of chances in the regular camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But during the death marches, and in those transit camps, it was a chaos already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Buchenwald in those days held-- my number in Buchenwald was 200 and some thousand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I don't even remember-- I remember my regular number.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But I don't remember exactly my regular-- my Buchenwald number.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I think it's 245,000 something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But anyway, and I knew I had to get out of this Buchenwald somehow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I-- I-- I saw horrible conditions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Rumors of cannibalism.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I never saw actual ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But I saw one time a bunch of Ukrainians or perhaps Belarusians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They were behind a barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They were cooking something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It wasn't-- it wasn't a beef, that's for sure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And it smelled awful, and two or three guys were kind of hanging around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And one of them would say, he say, don't tell me he's going-- he's-- I think he's going to eat that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Let me have a bite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Let me have a bite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And I just wondered what-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "It was-- it's either a rodent or-- or who knows what.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And it was ?] strictly starvation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "One time-- the meals were not anymore three times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "You wind up-- line up in-- in front of, of-- of all place, a movie theater.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
